      "rationale": "Reynolds number matched at primary design point (Re_CFD = 4820, Re_exp = 4780). Womersley number equivalency not assessed for pulsatile VAD operating mode. Exposure-time ratio between Lagrangian and Eulerian formulations not reconciled. Factor flagged as not-assessed epistemic gap critical to extrapolation validity."
    }
